import re

def find_phone_numbers(subject):
    pattern = '\\b([2-9]\\d{2})\\-([2-9]\\d{2})\\-(\\d{4})\\b'
    matches = re.findall(pattern, subject)
    return [f'{m[0]}{m[1]}-{m[2]}' for m in matches]
